deck: Finnish comic auteur. Real name Vilja Takalo.
description:
She was born in 1976.

She graduated from the university of applied sciences of Tampere in 2001, where she studied classic art.

Her first comic was kehä (I Ringen).

She identifies herself as a feminist, to some degree, and feminism has influenced her works greatly.

She publishes self-published comics frequently. She has been nminated for comic Finlandia (an appraised Finnish award) thrice.
name: Tiitu Takalo
